        <inline name="agenda item name">Consideration of prevention of transboundary harm from hazardous activities and allocation of loss in the case of such harm</inline>
      </p>
      <p>
        <docTitle>Resolution adopted by the General Assembly on 7 December 2022</docTitle>
      </p>
